<HL>
   Campeau Ousts
   Firm's Founder
   From Top Jobs
   ---
   Creditors' Representatives
   Are Temporarily Given
   Role of Chief Executive
   ----
   By Larry M. Greenberg
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
08/13/90
</DATE>
